{"tid":1556674,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Kill標王越野賽選手郭遠雄 山上尋回證實死亡","createTime":"2019-09-09T23:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T02:07:28.000Z","uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b2dd495b07b5b7724bba6e14ffcf48e77687f001","tid":1556674,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568071893_4c18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568071893_4c18.jpg&h=a5903e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n郭遠雄倒卧在斜坡上救起證實死亡。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n參加「Kill標王越野山賽2019」的32參賽者郭遠雄，失蹤逾32小時後，搜索人員於凌晨約1時20分，在沙田九肚山一斜坡發現郭，消防救將他救起，惟已證實死亡。案件列作屍體發現，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190910/60028162\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60028162&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=e6a7a081\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60028162&h=94571063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190910/60028162</a>"},{"pid":"67849ea863ef7273e6ce60daf3ed6588e3cdf583","tid":1556674,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:40:27.000Z","msg":"黑警又殺左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52733ee8e3f29b49efe0344cb0f06a088456c67","tid":1556674,"uid":68738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:43:19.000Z","msg":"突發緊急！係唔係有人求救緊？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553915</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n諗起呢單"},{"pid":"d6339cea81b155e60be3b40024369cd774abaac6","tid":1556674,"uid":40470,"lik